S

Show the DataEx optin Takeover activity. The activity will be started with Activity.startActivityForResult with a request code of REQUEST_TAKEOVER_STATUS. If you wish to act on the user completing onboarding (such as for analytic purposes), you can override Activity.onActivityResult and capture the result for REQUEST_TAKEOVER_STATUS.
